"From the <strong>Guest House App</strong>, you can manage your bookings.<br/"
">The\n"
"            Guest House App relies on the Rental and Planning Apps binding, "
"with a few\n"
"            customizations."
msgstr ""
"Du kan administrere dine bookinger via <strong>Gæstehusappen</strong>.<br/>\n"
"            Gæstehusappen er baseret på Udlejnings- og Planlægningsappen med "
"enkelte\n"
