#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:guest_house.product_template_18
msgid "Under-the-roof charm perfect for adventurous little dreamers."
msgstr "Loftets charme er perfekt til eventyrlystne små drømmere."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.homepage
msgid ""
"We strive to provide a unique experience, blending comfort with local charm. "
"Our commitment to hospitality ensures that every guest leaves with cherished "
"memories."
msgstr ""
"Vi stræber efter at give dig en unik oplevelse, hvor komfort møder lokal "
"charme. Vores engagement i gæstfrihed sikrer, at hver gæst rejser hjem med "
"værdifulde minder."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcome your guests as well from the <strong>Guest House App</strong>."
msgstr "Byd dine gæster velkommen fra <strong>Gæstehusappen</strong>."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:web_tour.tour,rainbow_man_message:guest_house.knowledge_tour
msgid "Welcome! Happy exploring."
msgstr "Velkommen! God fornøjelse med at gå på opdagelse."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Willing to upgrade a booking?"
msgstr "Vil du opgradere din reservation?"

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Vil du gerne tale med os om dit Odoo-setup eller drøfte nogle spørgsmål mere "
"detaljeret?"

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You are repairing a room or simply welcoming family and don't want guests to "
"book a room?"
msgstr ""
"Renoverer du et værelse, eller forventer du familiebesøg og ønsker ikke, at "
"gæster booker det?"

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilgå alle installerede apps i din Odoo-database direkte fra "
"hoveddashboardet."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your\n"
"                    Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Du har gennemført demoens brugsscenarie! Der findes millioner af måder at "
"tilpasse din Odoo-opsætning,\n"
"                    så den passer til dine forretningsbehov."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You could customize this section to add the identity document picture or "
"extra\n"
"                    fields at your convenience with studio. Just be careful, "
"such customizations can\n"
"                    quickly become messy."
msgstr ""
"Du kan tilpasse dette afsnit efter behov for at tilføje et billede af "
"identifikationsdokumentet eller ekstra\n"
"                    felter. Vær dog opmærksom på, at sådanne tilpasninger\n"
"                    hurtigt kan blive uoverskuelige."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt;\n"
"                    Upgrade your package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"Har du ikke importeret demodata endnu? Du kan stadig nå det. Gå til Apps &gt;"
" Brancher &gt;\n"
"                    Opgradér din pakke, og markér det relevante felt"

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "You guest house is online and future guests found it!"
msgstr "Dit gæstehus er nu online, og fremtidige gæster kan finde det!"

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "You have a future guest on the line willing to book a room?"
msgstr "Har du en potentiel gæst i røret, der ønsker at reservere et værelse?"

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Guest House package. By doing so, we have "
"installed a\n"
"            bunch of necessary apps to run your bar efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Du har lige installeret Odoo-pakken til gæstehuse, hvilket inkluderer en\n"
"            række nødvendige apps til effektiv drift af din bar."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may have noticed the city tax were added to the guest order from the "
"moment they\n"
"            checked in.<br/>This is because city taxes are to be billed to "
"spent nights in practice\n"
"            and not in theory.<br/>Let's adjust them now."
msgstr ""
"Du har måske bemærket, at turistskatten blev tilføjet til gæstebestillingen "
"fra tidspunktet for\n"
"            indtjekning.<br/>Dette skyldes, at turistskatten beregnes for "
"overnatningerne.\n"
"            <br/>Lad os justere dem nu."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "You might have tested this package with or without demo data."
msgstr "Du har muligvis testet denne pakke med eller uden demodata."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You noticed that the Identity Check highlights whether you captured all the\n"
"            necessary information for a guest?"
msgstr ""
"Har du bemærket, at identitetskontrollen viser, om alle\n"
"            nødvendige oplysninger for en gæst er indtastet?"

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You now know how to create a new order.<br/>Let's replicate the previous "
"steps but\n"
"                this time, without confirming the order (just saving it as "
"draft)."
msgstr ""
"Nu ved du, hvordan man opretter en ny reservation.<br/>Gentag trinnene,\n"
"                men gem den denne gang kun som udkast uden at bekræfte."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows\n"
"            you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Med denne pakke i Odoo kan du gennemføre følgende flows\n"
"for hurtigt at få overblik over de forskellige processer."

#. module: guest_house
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guest_house.welcome_article_body
msgid "You welcome your first guests, awesome!"
msgstr "Du byder nu dine første gæster velkommen, godt gået!"

